    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite seven assessed credibility factors each achieving one gradation below required level and six factors flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps at MRL 5, the assessment team determined that the Monte Carlo UQ bounds on hemolysis index remain below the absolute clinical threshold across all five operating points with 95% confidence. Conditional acceptance is granted subject to: (1) completion of the pending digital signature workflow to restore full structural integrity verification under ProfileComplete, (2) independent replication study within 12 months, and (3) post-market hemolysis surveillance at 6-month intervals. The package is filed under ProfileMinimal because the organisation signature infrastructure is not yet operational; the sha256 hash provides integrity traceability in the interim.",
